Describe webapi#sha1#sha1
  It computes SHA-1 of "abc"
    Assert Equals(webapi#sha1#sha1("abc"), "a9993e364706816aba3e25717850c26c9cd0d89d")
  End

  It computes SHA-1 of longer string
    Assert Equals(webapi#sha1#sha1("abcdbcdecdefdefgefghfghighijhijkijkljklmklmnlmnomnopnopq"), "84983e441c3bd26ebaae4aa1f95129e5e54670f1")
  End

  It computes SHA-1 of empty string
    Assert Equals(webapi#sha1#sha1(""), "da39a3ee5e6b4b0d3255bfef95601890afd80709")
  End
End
